    files & their extensions

        text file  					.txt
        PDF files					.pdf
        Pictures					.jpg, .png .gif, .tiff, etc
        word document				.doc
        excel files					.xlsx
        power point					.ppt
        java files					.java   (Source Code)
        java file                   .class  (Byte Code)


        how to open preference window:
        		windows:
        			file -> settings

        		Mac:
        			IntelliJ IDEA -> Preference


        		How to rename?
                        		right click -> refactor -> rename

                        		CamelCase
                        		JavaFile
                        		JavaProgrammingLanguage



                How to create project?
                        		File -> new -> Project

                package: used for storing java files in an organized manner

                        			right click src folder -> new  -> package

                        			package name starts with lower_case_letter

                Java File:
                        			right click PACKAGE -> new -> Java Class

                        			class name  starts with UpperCaseLetter

                        			CamelCase

                 ScreenShot  PRTSC     Win+Shift+S

                 System.out.println() : used for regular outputs (Black- Siyah )
                 System.err.println() : used for printing error messages ( Red Kirmizi)

                 Java is Case-Sensitive Language. Kucuk harf buyuk harf duyarli


                //Single line Comment

                /*
                Multi
                Line
                Comment
                 */

                 // CTRL+/    CMD+/


                Escape sequences: MUST be given with double quote

                 // \n  -> Yeni Satir - starts a new line
                 // \t  -> bir tab bosluk birakir - paragraph space(tab)
                 // \b  -> Backspace
                 // \"  -> "  double quote
                 // \r  -> Satir Basi
                 // \\  ->  \  single back slash